               <msContents>
                  <summary>Pp. 1-8 blank with scribbles and erased crude drawings of angels ;Pp. 9-52 Praise of Mary ውዳሴ ማርያም ;Pp. 9-12 of Monday ዘሰኑይ ;Pp. 13-20 of Tuesday ዘሠሉስ ; Pp. 20-27 of Wednesdayዘረቡዕ ;Pp. 27-36 of Thursday ዘሐሙስ ;Pp. 36-42 of Friday ዘአርብ ;Pp. 42-46 of Saturday ዘቀዳሚት ሰንበት ;Pp. 47-52 of Sunday ዘሰንበተ ክርስቲያን ;Pp. 52-71 The Gate of Light አንቀጸ ብርሃን ;Pp. 71-75 The Angels Praise Mary (Yewedeswa Mala'ekt) (it starts from the Wabasades) ይዌድስዋ መላእክት ;Pp. 76-101 Image of Mary መልክአ ማርያም ;Pp.101-126 Image of Jesus መልክአ ኢየሱስ ;Pp. 127 blank ;Pp. 128 Drawing of the Virgin Mary 'with her beloved son' in pencil and ink
                  </summary>
                  
                  
               </msContents>
